snippet: Tricia Liston scored 20 points, and Haley Peters had 17 points and a career-high 20 rebounds as No. 2 Duke beat visiting South Carolina-Upstate, 123-40.
abstract: Duke routs South Carolina-Upstate, 123-40, in women's college basketball.
